    "ultimate": {
      "name": "Phantom Steed",
      "description": "Leomord summons (Barbiel) to rush to him, knocking back and dealing 350( +100% Total Physical Attack) (Physical Damage) to all enemies in its path. If (Barbiel) comes in contact with Leomord, they will enter the Mounted State, gaining 30% Movement Speed that decays over 2s. (Mounted State): Leomord gains a brand-new set of skills, and his Basic Attack can be used while moving and hits a circular area to deal AOE damage. Leomord also gains 60 Movement Speed and 30 Physical & Magic Defense.",
